what_worked: Applied prefetch_fact_join, multi_dimension_prefetch, single_pass_aggregation: Prefiltered item and date_dim tables into CTEs, then pre-joined them with store_sales in a filtered_fact CTE before joining remaining dimensions. This reduces the fact table early and applies selective filters before expensive multi-way joins.
why_it_worked: Pre-joining filtered dimensions with fact table before aggregation reduces join input; Pre-filtering multiple dimension tables in parallel reduces join fan-out; Consolidating repeated scans into CASE aggregates reduces I/O from N scans to 1
